A client-server application for calculating sums and products of all integers between two selected (inclusive) numbers from the range 1 to 1000.

# Build client image
docker build -t calc-client -f Dockerfile .

# The server is started in the calculation-net network
# Wait for the server to start

To start the client:
# Start the client in the calculation-net network
docker run -it --rm --name calculation-client --network calculation-net -e SERVER_HOST=calculation-server calc-client
